transposition to our line.}) 12. h4 $5 {I like this direct move. We've got a
passer down there, let's roll this pawn all the way up!} ({In case} 12. Qd3 d4
13. h4 {black has an extra option} b6 $5) 12... Bd7 (12... d4 13. h5 $14) 13.
h5 O-O-O {Now we need to play} (13... d4 14. Qd3) 14. Qd3 {[#]} ({otherwise
