stuff with moves like ...f7-f6 or ...Nxe5, but those aren't easy to make work.}
14... Nf5 ({Another possibility would be} 14... d4 {This looks active but
doesn't stop White from pursuing his plan} 15. h6 {[#]} Be8 (15... Kb8 16. h7
Rh8 17. Rb1 Bc8 18. g4 b6 19. Bg2 {The h7-pawn is strong. Not only is that an
