improvement with} 19... Rg7 20. Qxa7 (20. Bd3 Nf5) 20... Rgxh7 21. Rxh7 Rxh7 {
[#]} 22. Qa8+ Qb8 23. Qxb8+ Kxb8 24. Be3 {White's got an extra pawn and a
bishop pair. However, the material has been significantly reduced, so possibly
Black has chances to hold a draw with some extremely precise play.} Rh1 (24...
Be4 $5 $132) 25. Kf2 Nd5 26. Rd1 Ba4 27. Be2 Rh2 28. Rxd5 exd5 29. Bd3 d4 $2 ({
